  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to investigate whether finnish binding pancreatico-jejunal
      anastomosis is feasible and prevents the risk for post operative pancreatic fistula after
      distal pancreeatectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
